Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.55,0:16:30.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,0)\shad1\fs22\bord1.5\an8\u1}Shoes:{\u0}\NNagi
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.42,0:01:33.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The keeper of the Kannagi Shrine?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.60,0:01:36.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think you can ask the shrine's prefecture office,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.99,0:01:38.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but why do you want to research this?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.07,0:01:43.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well... I'm just curious to know more about the shrine nearby.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.65,0:01:46.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I'm impressed.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.35,0:01:49.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I never knew you were such a passionate student.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.05,0:01:51.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give me a moment, I'll ask for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.25,0:01:52.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry for the trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.14,0:01:57.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.60,0:02:01.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.06,0:02:07.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jin.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.14,0:02:08.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Daitetsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.72,0:02:11.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come with me for a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.44,0:02:13.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.76,0:02:17.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know we shouldn't be seeing each other...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.13,0:02:19.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.18,0:02:20.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.58,0:02:25.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Nagi's...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.46,0:02:28.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I picked it up just now.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.93,0:02:33.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was on the rooftop, since I would cause another ruckus if I went to the club room...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.80,0:02:39.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, I found it...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.79,0:02:54.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She... I can't find any signs of her anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.96,0:02:59.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see... There's no helping her.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.42,0:03:01.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks. I'll return it to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.22,0:03:04.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did something happen between you and Nagi-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.63,0:03:05.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nope, it's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.41,0:03:09.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We had a little fight, but that happens all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.26,0:03:25.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah... You're from the school... for homework...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.08,0:03:27.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cute boy!{tlc: menkoigo da}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.73,0:03:29.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come, come! Come in, Come in!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.52,0:03:33.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Want some rice cakes with bean paste?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.24,0:03:35.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.99,0:03:38.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Which school are you from? {is he asking where his school is located? or which school?}{est: which/where either works, since schools are named by place}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.71,0:03:39.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Umm...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.20,0:03:40.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have boiled chestnuts, want some?{est: it might be 'kuri nitano' (boiled chestnuts) or 'kuri muitano' (peeled chesnuts)}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.71,0:03:44.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These are ferns that I picked from the mountains!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.97,0:03:45.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Want any dried potatoes?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.35,0:03:47.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How old are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.87,0:03:49.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Want some sweets?{karintosan}{est: karintou are sweets}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.52,0:03:50.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm fine, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.33,0:03:53.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.14,0:03:57.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My husband longs for company ever since our sons left home.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.26,0:03:58.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please play along with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.71,0:04:00.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay. Umm...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.20,0:04:03.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our second{tlc} son went to that high school,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.06,0:04:05.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but he failed the university entrance exam and became a private candidate{this could be a purely UK term, please check} for two years.{est: he failed entrance exams, and failed again the next year,}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.90,0:04:08.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He went to a vocational school after that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.53,0:04:11.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But all of a sudden, he said he wanted to study overseas.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.73,0:04:14.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Umm, what was it? Hey, dear...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.80,0:04:18.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He went to some country in the south.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.02,0:04:22.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Later, he met a girl in a bar and is going to marry her, or something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.97,0:04:23.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Want some rice crackers?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.18,0:04:26.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to ask about the shrine...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.19,0:04:28.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kannagi Shrine?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.90,0:04:34.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that place has always been managed by the five families living around here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.11,0:04:38.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Satous over there, and the Suzukis, and also the Tanakas!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.36,0:04:41.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doesn't it have a Shinto priest?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.00,0:04:42.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.58,0:04:44.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We get one from another place to make a trip here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.66,0:04:47.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Apparently, there were ancient documents stored here,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.75,0:04:50.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but they got destroyed in a fire long ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.62,0:04:56.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why nobody knows the name of the god enshrined here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.08,0:05:01.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our Oba{m}a-sama{not her grandma, i also dunno what to put}{est: Old lady? (it's probably her mother)} is the only one who might know something.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.80,0:05:06.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Obaa-chan? Obaa-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.47,0:05:10.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This child wants to hear about Kannagi-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.56,0:05:26.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Umm...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.81,0:05:29.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, she actually can hear us.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.13,0:05:37.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm grateful to Kannagi-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.92,0:05:43.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She also saved the people who tried to hang themselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.51,0:05:46.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Hang themselves?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.85,0:05:49.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. It was events during the war.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.81,0:05:54.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Life was hard, so there were people who did that, or so I heard.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.76,0:05:56.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It used to be a deserted place.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.89,0:05:59.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But that's all in the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.10,0:06:03.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Obaa-chan always talks about such things.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.18,0:06:11.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.72,0:06:15.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lately, I've seen you a lot on TV.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.59,0:06:17.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you still cost 100 yen?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.50,0:06:19.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's quite some spirit of service you have there.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.37,0:06:23.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're willing to pay a hundred thousand for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.60,0:06:26.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you want money, you'll get more out of playing with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.96,0:06:29.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've got it wrong, I'm not like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.60,0:06:40.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't I tell you I'm not like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.04,0:06:44.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What's with this bitch?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.38,0:06:48.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn, don't get all cocky just because we went easy on you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.25,0:06:52.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.81,0:06:57.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ouch, ouch, ouch...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.54,0:06:59.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You bitch, don't fuck wit—
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.55,0:07:01.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys, go from that side!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.16,0:07:03.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, wait a sec—
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.12,0:07:06.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can get more out of playing with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.74,0:07:09.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't even get any fun out of you guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.84,0:07:10.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.25,0:07:14.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey. Take this man with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.76,0:07:24.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eww, they're dirty. My shoes are soiled.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.08,0:07:26.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you all right, Zange-chan? {Naboo~}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.91,0:07:30.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry that I wasn't of any help... {Naboo~}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.37,0:07:33.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look, I bought you a canned coffee. {Naboo~}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.67,0:07:37.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kyaa! Mister, thanks as always!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.46,0:07:42.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mister will do anything for you, Zange-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.40,0:07:45.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you're so mean to hide in a corner and watch.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.70,0:07:48.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was so afraid!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.10,0:07:52.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mister is weak against violence... {nabooooo}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.47,0:07:57.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're strong...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.09,0:08:01.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't say that, it was all by chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.05,0:08:04.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was imitating the kung-fu movies and I hit them by chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.98,0:08:08.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With her skills, I didn't even need to save her back there...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.06,0:08:12.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so happy that you came to find me today.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.43,0:08:14.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was always me looking for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.92,0:08:17.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.73,0:08:18.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ferns...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.10,0:08:23.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I came to ask you something concerning Nagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.66,0:08:26.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have many doubts...{est: things unsure of}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.67,0:08:30.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're asking whether we're really gods?{est: she's}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.31,0:08:34.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I see. Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.61,0:08:35.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If it's concerning Nee-sama...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.65,0:08:40.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.29,0:08:44.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...a woman's secret.{est: girl}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.55,0:08:47.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A se-cr-et!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.42,0:08:49.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.01,0:08:55.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For the impurities that I hunt, I seal them up like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.63,0:08:59.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though it's a watering can, it's used for sprinkling holy water.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.48,0:09:04.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I put them in such a thing, they can't get away.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.32,0:09:09.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since the impurities will taint the land, they have to be eliminated.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.90,0:09:12.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And a god has the duty to do so.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.94,0:09:15.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is what I recognize.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.90,0:09:19.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know anything beyond that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.63,0:09:21.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She gave the same response as Nagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.93,0:09:24.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But are you not bothered by that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.80,0:09:26.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not important.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.03,0:09:33.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As I've told you before, my goal is to become an individualist.{est: hmm... XD word choice... watashirashii is an often used word but I can't TL it well orz}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.56,0:09:37.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have little interest in anything else.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.91,0:09:41.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As long as I remain a god, all is well.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.05,0:09:43.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what I feel.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.62,0:09:48.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But do you have any proof that you're truly a god?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.80,0:09:50.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're unusually concerned about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.40,0:09:54.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever gave you the idea that we're not?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.98,0:09:58.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The truth is... Suzushiro-sensei said...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.24,0:10:01.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Lowly spirits?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.62,0:10:04.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's just like him to think like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.02,0:10:10.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In the first place, it's wrong to speak of Japan's gods from the perspective of western theology.{est: western view of god}{神学的視点？　見当はずれ？ And Zange-chan, don't say that while wearing your sister cosplay}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.11,0:10:17.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei said that there were cases of such spirits that believed themselves to be gods.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.60,0:10:20.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That got me a little confused...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.39,0:10:22.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.97,0:10:26.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In this world, there are many things that have ambiguity as their charm.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.39,0:10:32.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,D-Don't tell me... Jin-kun, you're not suspecting me, are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.00,0:10:33.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.34,0:10:36.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm really a god, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.45,0:10:37.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.18,0:10:39.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't believe me, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.61,0:10:44.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I can't say the same about that dumb sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.73,0:10:48.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In Nee-sama's case, her method of taking form is {super}special{, that's why you are here with me}.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.34,0:10:56.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A sacred tree is something that possesses great spiritual power.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.28,0:11:01.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As a vessel that houses a god, it's a plant with excellent potential.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.41,0:11:07.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But that also means it'll attract random spirits.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.49,0:11:13.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Some unknown spirit from God knows where might be pretending to be Nee-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.73,0:11:15.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Such a thing is possible too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.74,0:11:17.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what I think.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.62,0:11:18.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.19,0:11:34.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Life was hard, so there were people who did that, or so I heard.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.89,0:11:37.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll attract random spirits.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.25,0:11:42.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Some unknown spirit from God knows where might be pretending to be Nee-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.10,0:11:47.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Either they are speaking as gods solely for their own ends,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.84,0:11:51.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,or they falsely believe that they themselves are gods.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.05,0:11:54.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It all makes sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.37,0:12:12.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nagi?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.68,0:13:15.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you have to do this?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.78,0:13:43.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You were lying to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.52,0:13:50.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.55,0:15:05.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to go to school.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.28,0:15:57.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did she...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.21,0:16:04.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did she really exist in the first place?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.39,0:16:06.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.37,0:16:33.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.12,0:16:34.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.97,0:16:38.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing here? This place is for the second-year students. {wait, nagi is second year?}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.70,0:16:39.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.48,0:16:42.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gosh, what's wrong? You didn't sleep at all?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.11,0:16:47.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's Nagi-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.76,0:16:50.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No idea. She may be absent today.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.89,0:16:52.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Weren't you with her?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.80,0:16:53.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.62,0:17:13.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nagi-sama? She's not here yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.33,0:17:15.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.81,0:17:18.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Senpai, have you seen her around?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.37,0:17:22.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nagi-sama? I haven't. Are you looking for her?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.73,0:17:23.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.62,0:17:25.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shino, Akiba-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.37,0:17:26.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you seen Nagi-sama?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.05,0:17:28.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.00,0:17:29.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't seen her.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.22,0:17:31.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong? You two had a quarrel?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.11,0:17:36.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, but please let me skip club today.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.91,0:17:39.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Wait... Mikuriya?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.56,0:17:43.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doesn't that sound serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.86,0:17:46.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did something happen between those two?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.28,0:17:48.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't think...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.73,0:17:51.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Perhaps they're getting into a gal-game kind of development?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.49,0:17:53.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How can that be?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.74,0:17:56.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But does Mikuriya have the guts to do such a thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.11,0:17:58.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He doesn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.16,0:18:01.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But boys of that age are all wolves!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.16,0:18:04.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't know what might make them go wild!{tlc. what's she saying?}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.02,0:18:07.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Takako, you're more like a wolf yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.55,0:18:10.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mikuriya, I believe in you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.83,0:18:13.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jin!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.00,0:18:16.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's Nagi-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.98,0:18:18.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's absent, haven't I told you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.89,0:18:21.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is she sick? Should I go and make her porridge?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.99,0:18:23.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.93,0:18:25.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's not sick...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.44,0:18:28.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not yourself today.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.71,0:18:30.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me if something happened.{est: Tell me if something happened}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.84,0:18:37.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, but I'll be going home.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.02,0:18:37.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jin?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.68,0:19:42.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jin!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{est: (typeset on phone after above one) One missed call}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.60,0:21:13.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jin...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.60,0:21:27.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to run away...{est: You don't have to run away...}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.78,0:21:33.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what's wrong with Nagi-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.74,0:21:35.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.49,0:21:36.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Today's the second day.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.31,0:21:41.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, did something really happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.21,0:21:43.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wasn't it an illness?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.50,0:21:45.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's happened? Did you have a fight with her?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.30,0:21:47.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Playing truant?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.12,0:21:48.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.67,0:21:55.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...may not...{est: ...may not...}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.50,0:22:01.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She may not be coming back.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.08,0:23:39.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please watch the next episode of Kannagi too!
